      <para id="id1583593">[LO 1.3]</para>
      <para id="id8251408">Assignment 4</para>
      <para id="id812502">By using shading and colouring pencils, add dimension to the figures in assignment 3. The light falls from the top left, just behind the figures (<emphasis effect="italics">a</emphasis> offers a clue).</para>
      <para id="id1713690">[LO 1.3]</para>
      <para id="id4531107">Assignment 5</para>
      <para id="id1405367">Design a simple pattern to be used as a stencil for applying the pattern to the outside of your container in different coloured koki pens. Each design may not exceed 3 cm by 3 cm. Design a pattern in each of the following squares and circle your final choice in blue.</para>
      <para id="id1166972105268">(Remember: keep the design simple, as you will be using sharp scissors to cut the pattern from a stencil-plate.)</para>
