      <para id="id7662440">Assignment 6</para>
      <para id="id4329352">Write down the correct answer:</para>
      <list id="id1166967505229" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha" mark-prefix="(" mark-suffix=")">
        <item>What type of line is easier to cut from plastic?</item>
      </list>
      <para id="id1166971748132">straight, bent</para>
      <list id="id2257542" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha" mark-prefix="(" mark-suffix=")">
        <item>What type of corner is easier to cut from plastic?</item>
      </list>
      <para id="id1166967367611">sharp, rounded</para>
      <list id="id1999056" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha" mark-prefix="(" mark-suffix=")">
        <item>Choose the most difficult design in red and give a reason for your answer:</item>
        <item>Choose any of your designs and write something negative and something positive about the particular design.</item>
      </list>
      <para id="id1166963189426">Your choice: [Letter]</para>
      <para id="id6676776">[LO 1.10]</para>
      <list id="id6161999" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha" mark-prefix="(" mark-suffix=")">
        <item>Staple the stencil pattern on a sheet of paper or in your workbook after use.</item>
